1
00:00:19,916 --> 00:00:20,916
Good morning!

2
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:22,166
How's it goin'?

3
00:00:27,875 --> 00:00:29,125
Man, am I tired.

4
00:00:29,208 --> 00:00:30,916
Hey, good morning
to you, Tsukune.

5
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,625
Oh, 'morning, guys.

6
00:00:32,708 --> 00:00:35,166
So, are both of your parents
showin' up today or just one?

7
00:00:35,250 --> 00:00:36,041
Huh?

8
00:00:36,125 --> 00:00:37,125
My parents?

9
00:00:37,208 --> 00:00:38,708
Hold on, what are
you talking about?

10
00:00:38,791 --> 00:00:41,375
'Kay?

11
00:00:41,458 --> 00:00:44,250
And since tomorrow is
Yokai Academy's Parents' Day...

12
00:00:44,333 --> 00:00:46,541
All of you need to show your
folks what a great school

13
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:48,916
this is, so let's do it
and I'll see you and them

14
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,500
in the morning!

15
00:00:50,583 --> 00:00:52,791
Right...

16
00:00:52,875 --> 00:00:53,791
Neither.

17
00:00:53,875 --> 00:00:55,375
Huh?!

18
00:00:55,458 --> 00:00:58,041
Uh, I mean "neither 'cause my
parents are way too super-busy

19
00:00:58,125 --> 00:01:00,291
to come!"
Yeah, that's what I meant!

20
00:01:00,375 --> 00:01:01,666
Dude, that rocks!

21
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:03,166
Huh?

22
00:01:03,250 --> 00:01:04,666
This guy's parents trust him
so much that they don't need

23
00:01:04,750 --> 00:01:07,083
to come see him at school...!
I wish my parents

24
00:01:07,166 --> 00:01:08,666
treated me like an adult!

25
00:01:08,750 --> 00:01:11,208
I'm really lucky!

26
00:01:11,291 --> 00:01:13,291
And a human with
human parents...

27
00:01:13,375 --> 00:01:15,166
That's why I didn't
tell 'em about today!

28
00:01:15,250 --> 00:01:17,458
I really would've liked
to have met your mom, though.

29
00:01:17,541 --> 00:01:18,041
Huh?

30
00:01:18,125 --> 00:01:18,875
Yeah, me, too!

31
00:01:18,958 --> 00:01:20,625
You wanna meet my Mom?!

32
00:01:20,708 --> 00:01:21,666
I sure would!

33
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:22,916
Huh?!

34
00:01:24,583 --> 00:01:27,083
I really would've liked to have
met your mother, too, Tsukune;

35
00:01:27,166 --> 00:01:29,833
it would have been so nice.

36
00:01:29,916 --> 00:01:32,333
I really would've liked to have
met your mother, too, Tsukune;

37
00:01:32,416 --> 00:01:36,041
it would have been
so nice; I'd say...

38
00:01:36,125 --> 00:01:37,791
No, I'll take care of
dinner, Mrs. Aono,

39
00:01:37,875 --> 00:01:40,041
and do you mind
if I call you "Mom?"

40
