Hi, sweetie!

56
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:04,875
Mommy!

57
00:04:04,958 --> 00:04:05,625
Daddy!

58
00:04:05,708 --> 00:04:07,333
--"Mommy?"
--"Daddy?"

59
00:04:07,416 --> 00:04:08,833
You're late!

60
00:04:08,916 --> 00:04:10,041
I was worried you'd gotten into
a boo-boo and was about to

61
00:04:10,125 --> 00:04:11,291
cry my eyes out!

62
00:04:11,375 --> 00:04:14,583
Ha, ha, sorry 'bout that, son.

63
00:04:14,666 --> 00:04:16,416
