64
00:04:17,541 --> 00:04:20,000
It's just me, so I better
get to Kokoa's classroom

65
00:04:20,083 --> 00:04:21,458
and spend some time with her.

66
00:04:21,541 --> 00:04:22,958
Just you?

67
00:04:23,041 --> 00:04:25,250
Yeah, you see, the truth
is, I've never once had

68
00:04:25,333 --> 00:04:27,708
anyone come and visit
me on Parents' Day...

69
00:04:27,791 --> 00:04:31,875
it's the same for Kokoa
so I thought I'd go visit her.

70
00:04:31,958 --> 00:04:33,333
Oh, Moka...

71
00:04:33,416 --> 00:04:35,083
I don't need your charity!

72
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:36,333
Ya hear?!

73
00:04:37,541 --> 00:04:39,500
If you even think of
coming to my classroom,

74
00:04:39,583 --> 00:04:41,208
you're gonna meet the
business end of my little

75
00:04:41,291 --> 00:04:43,833
Ko hammer here,
and you're so gonna regret it!

76
00:04:43,916 --> 00:04:44,708
Hmph!

77
00:04:44,791 --> 00:04:46,250
Well, I certainly regret it...

78
00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:47,666
Agh! Tsukune!

79
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:54,041
Are you okay...? I'm sorry;
you got hurt because of me.

80
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:55,291
It's not your fault...

81
00:04:55,375 --> 00:04:57,333
But what was that stuff
you were saying before?

82
00:04:57,416 --> 00:05:00,458
About how no one ever came
to see you on Parents' Day?

83
00:05:11,375 --> 00:05:13,291
It's been like that
since I was little.

84
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:14,500
I'm used to it.

85
00:05:14,583 --> 00:05:16,208
I'm always the only one
nobody comes to see.

86
00:05:16,291 --> 00:05:19,083
But Moka...

87
00:05:19,166 --> 00:05:20,166
Not this year.

88
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:21,208
Huh?

89
00:05:21,291 --> 00:05:23,250
Nobody's coming
to see me, either...

90
00:05:23,333 --> 00:05:25,416
We're in the same boat.

91
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,750
Oh, Tsukune...

92
00:05:26,833 --> 00:05:28,958
Oh, Moka...

93
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:30,750
Oh, Tsukune...

94
00:05:35,541 --> 00:05:37,166
My blood, huh?

95
00:05:41,416 --> 00:05:43,750
PDA's are against
school rules, you know...?

96
00:05:43,833 --> 00:05:46,208
Do you mind telling me
what you're doing here, Moka?

97
00:05:46,291 --> 00:05:50,083
I should be asking you what
you're doing here, stalker!

98
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:52,541
It's because I want
to ask Tsukune a favor.

99
00:05:52,625 --> 00:05:53,708
Huh?

100
00:05:53,791 --> 00:05:55,166
It's my dumb mother;
she keeps nagging me

101
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:56,833
to introduce you to her.

102
00:05:56,916 --> 00:05:59,375
Me? Um, sure.
Where is she...? Well?

103
00:06:04,625 --> 00:06:06,291
She's been here
the whole time?!

104
00:06:06,375 --> 00:06:09,083
Now I see where
Mizore gets that from!

105
00:06:09,166 --> 00:06:11,916
Mizore really takes after
her mother, doesn't she?!

106
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,125
Yeah...!

107
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:14,750
Hey, it's okay to
come out now, Mother...

108
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:16,000
This guy is my boyfriend.

109
00:06:16,083 --> 00:06:17,791
What?!

110
00:06:17,875 --> 00:06:19,000
Hey, hold on a second here!

111
00:06:19,083 --> 00:06:20,500
I'm not your-...!

112
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:21,875
Sorry, but could you please
play along and pretend to be

113
00:06:21,958 --> 00:06:24,625
my boyfriend for now...?
'Cause I kinda accidentally

114
00:06:24,708 --> 00:06:26,416
told my mom that you
and me were an item.

115
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,291
You what?!

116
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:28,333
Pleased to meet you...

117
00:06:28,416 --> 00:06:30,541
I'm Mizore's mother, Tsurara.

118
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,083
And you must be the
famous Tsukune, huh?

119
00:06:34,166 --> 00:06:37,041
You're even more handsome
than Mizore described.

120
00:06:37,125 --> 00:06:38,666
Uhhh!

121
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:39,916
Wow!

122
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,875
Mizore's mom seems
really classy and nice...

123
00:06:41,958 --> 00:06:43,375
Not to mention gorgeous!

124
00:06:43,458 --> 00:06:45,625
I can see where Mizore
gets her looks...

125
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:50,291
But I don't think
Moka's as impressed!

126
00:06:50,375 --> 00:06:52,708
Geez, it was going so good
there for a second.

127
00:06:52,791 --> 00:06:54,791
Why does this always
happen to us...?

128
00:06:54,875 --> 00:06:58,208
Still, it was sweet how Tsukune
said we were in the same boat...

129
00:06:58,291 --> 00:07:00,041
And who might this
nice young lady be?

130
00:07:00,125 --> 00:07:01,375
Huh?

131
00:07:01,458 --> 00:07:03,500
Oh! It's such a pleasure
to meet you, ma'am. I'm--

132
00:07:03,583 --> 00:07:05,416
She's just this
super clingy groupie girl.

133
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,916
Huh?

134
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,083
She's always spying on Tsukune
like some creepy stalker.

135
00:07:09,166 --> 00:07:10,791
You're the stalker!

136
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:15,500
Oh, Tsukune...! I found
you...! Yes...! Finally...!

137
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:18,541
Hey, Mom, quick,
he's over here!

138
00:07:18,625 --> 00:07:20,083
This is my mother.

139
00:07:20,166 --> 00:07:23,583
Please, call me Ageha...! So
you're Kurumu's fiancée, huh?

140
00:07:23,666 --> 00:07:25,791
--He's a fiancée this time?!
--I'm a fiancée this time?!

141
00:07:25,875 --> 00:07:27,250
And who might you be, dear?

142
00:07:27,333 --> 00:07:28,416
His wannabe lover?

143
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,958
Oh, I do certainly
hope so, Ms. Kurono!

144
00:07:31,041 --> 00:07:33,000
I see!

145
00:07:33,083 --> 00:07:35,208
I can't believe how
soft these things are...!

146
00:07:35,291 --> 00:07:37,875
Man, they're even
softer than Kurumu's!

147
00:07:37,958 --> 00:07:39,500
That daughter of mine...

148
00:07:39,583 --> 00:07:40,166
Huh?

149
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:41,500
You know, Kurumu...

150
00:07:41,583 --> 00:07:43,250
She might act suggestively...

151
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:46,041
but in actuality, she doesn't
have any real experience

152
00:07:46,125 --> 00:07:49,083
underneath the sheets,
now does she?

153
00:07:49,166 --> 00:07:50,458
So then...

154
00:07:50,541 --> 00:07:53,041
I'd appreciate it if you
gave her a roll in the hay.

155
00:07:54,666 --> 00:07:56,416
Wait, you mean
you want me to-...?!

156
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:58,666
What do you say
to dinner sometime?

157
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:00,416
You seem to need
some lessons in love

158
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:03,041
and I could give you
some hands-on instruction.

159
00:08:04,791 --> 00:08:05,500
There he is!

160
00:08:05,583 --> 00:08:06,625
Hey, Tsukune!

161
00:08:06,708 --> 00:08:08,458
Pardon us, please...

162
00:08:08,541 --> 00:08:11,125
And this, folks, is one of
our sophomore classrooms.

163
00:08:11,208 --> 00:08:12,291
Hey Rubi?

164
00:08:12,375 --> 00:08:13,250
why are you...?

165
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:14,416
Huh?

166
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:15,666
Fellow witches!

167
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,333
Oh, I'm so happy to meet you!

168
00:08:17,416 --> 00:08:18,666
I don't know how many
years it's been

169
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,541
since I've seen adult witches!

170
00:08:20,625 --> 00:08:21,791
Hey, paws off, you cougar!

171
00:08:21,875 --> 00:08:23,791
Tsukune's all mine!

172
00:08:26,250 --> 00:08:27,541
Tsurara?!

173
00:08:27,625 --> 00:08:28,958
Huh?!

174
00:08:30,708 --> 00:08:33,958
Well, is everyone having
an enjoyable Parents' Day?

175
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:37,750
