176
00:08:37,833 --> 00:08:40,000
Terrific; it's her!

177
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:50,875
That brings first period to
a close; now it's time for PE...

178
00:08:50,958 --> 00:08:53,750
Parents, if you'll head out
to the tennis courts, please!

179
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:08,541
