you guys were saying...!

180
00:09:08,625 --> 00:09:10,750
What the heck
is going on here?!

181
00:09:10,833 --> 00:09:12,000
Yeah, exactly.

182
00:09:12,083 --> 00:09:14,375
What was the deal with
all that "fiancée" crap?

183
