did the same thing!

186
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,500
I guess...

187
00:09:22,583 --> 00:09:25,291
But I know that me and Tsukune
are gonna hook up any day now.

188
00:09:25,375 --> 00:09:26,791
No way, he's gonna marry me!

189
00:09:26,875 --> 00:09:28,791
Whoa, wait, stop it! Just
hold on a minute and listen!

190
00:09:28,875 --> 00:09:32,208
Both of you guys need to go tell
your moms the truth right now!

191
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,958
Quiver, quiver;
quiver quiver...

192
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:43,583
You've just gotta
be my boyfriend!

193
00:09:43,666 --> 00:09:46,125
Please be my fiancée! He's
mine, abominable snowwoman!

194
00:09:46,958 --> 00:09:50,166
And now it's the second period
of Parents' Day, whee!

195
00:09:51,958 --> 00:09:53,958
Did you guys
just see my swing?!

196
00:09:59,875 --> 00:10:02,458
Nice save, Moka...!
That was great!

197
00:10:03,625 --> 00:10:05,000
Dang!

198
00:10:07,125 --> 00:10:09,416
Hey, a little effort
would be nice!

199
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,750
I melt when I run.

200
00:10:10,833 --> 00:10:11,666
"Melt?"

201
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,791
--Mizore!
--Honey!

202
00:10:12,875 --> 00:10:14,083
--Huh?
--Huh?

203
00:10:16,125 --> 00:10:18,291
What I want to know is how far
you've gone with Tsukune,

204
00:10:18,375 --> 00:10:18,916
