205
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,916
Uh...

206
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,166
What do you mean, Mom?!

207
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:22,958
Do it with him!

208
00:10:23,041 --> 00:10:24,916
Right here and
right now, okay?!

209
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,958
What?!

210
00:10:27,041 --> 00:10:28,958
But we're in the
middle of PE right now...

211
00:10:29,041 --> 00:10:31,166
And besides that, I've really
been trying to get Tsukune

212
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:34,250
to like me without having to use
any of my succubus powers...

213
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:36,666
Plus he and I haven't
even really kissed yet.

214
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,125
It sounds like your
relationship with him

215
00:10:38,208 --> 00:10:40,625
is over before it even started.

216
00:10:40,708 --> 00:10:41,708
Mom!

217
00:10:41,791 --> 00:10:43,916
If you want him,
do it with him, got it?!

218
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,291
Uh!

219
00:10:47,875 --> 00:10:50,500
Now Tsukune's gonna be
Kurumu's for sure.

220
00:10:50,583 --> 00:10:52,250
I want to talk to you about
the relationship that

221
00:10:52,333 --> 00:10:53,708
you have with Tsukune.

222
00:10:53,791 --> 00:10:55,750
There's something I need
to tell you about that.

223
00:10:55,833 --> 00:10:57,625
I want you to
freeze him, dear.

224
00:10:57,708 --> 00:11:00,083
Well, that wasn't what
I expected you to say.

225
00:11:00,166 --> 00:11:02,291
Mizore, if you freeze him
right now, then Tsukune

226
00:11:02,375 --> 00:11:04,541
will remain your
boyfriend forever.

227
00:11:04,625 --> 00:11:06,541
But, Mother, I made a promise
to him that I wouldn't

228
00:11:06,625 --> 00:11:08,416
do stuff like that anymore.

229
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,708
Really...? In that case,
don't be surprised if

230
00:11:10,791 --> 00:11:12,291
he ends up with Kurumu.

231
00:11:12,375 --> 00:11:13,000
No!

232
00:11:13,083 --> 00:11:15,250
I can't let that happen!

233
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:17,708
There's only one way to
make sure that it doesn't...

234
00:11:17,791 --> 00:11:21,541
And that's by freezing him
and keeping him close.

235
00:11:21,625 --> 00:11:24,541
That's the proper form
of love for a snow woman.

236
00:11:24,625 --> 00:11:25,208
Then...

237
00:11:25,291 --> 00:11:26,458
That's what I'll do.

238
00:11:27,541 --> 00:11:30,333
Now Tsukune's gonna
be Mizore's for sure.

239
00:11:30,416 --> 00:11:32,458
I will not lose
to that woman...

240
00:11:32,541 --> 00:11:35,000
I refuse to lose to her...

241
00:11:36,708 --> 00:11:39,625
Boy, these are some
scary mothers, whee!

242
00:11:53,458 --> 00:11:55,000
Tsukune, c'mere.

243
00:11:55,083 --> 00:11:56,083
Uh...

244
00:11:57,750 --> 00:12:00,041
What's keeping you,
Tsukune...? Hurry up.

245
00:12:00,125 --> 00:12:01,875
There's something
I want to do to you.

246
00:12:01,958 --> 00:12:04,208
Oh, yeah, and
what might that be?

247
00:12:04,291 --> 00:12:06,250
Oh, just this!

248
00:12:06,333 --> 00:12:07,583
No...! Oh, Tsukune!

249
00:12:07,666 --> 00:12:09,083
Hey, just what are you

250
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:10,250
--Hold on, I'll get you out...
--trying to do, kill him?!

251
00:12:10,333 --> 00:12:11,791
--It was love.
--Yeah, in what universe?!

252
00:12:11,875 --> 00:12:13,750
If I hadn't done it,
I might've lost him.

253
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:16,375
Just hold on
a little bit longer, Tsukune!

254
00:12:19,708 --> 00:12:21,958
Oh, thank goodness!

255
00:12:22,041 --> 00:12:24,041
I'm so grateful
that you're still alive!

256
00:12:24,125 --> 00:12:25,833
